(5855, 75393, 'THE BATON', 'START OF THE DAY''s new EP release "BATON" leads you back to the beginning. Blending together Scandinavian post-rock and shoegazer taste to create a sense of vast emotion; START OF THE DAY becomes an orchestra made out of a band with strings, keys, percussion, and vocals. Despite the absence of a solid bassist, START OF THE DAY''s sound is tighter than ever with a sense of unity among its compositions. The lead song "Paradise of Wonderland" comprises of a melody that makes you want to dance and vocals of angelic quality. Crossing all genres, their sound resounds in the hearts of their listeners. Having progressed as a band by touring outside of and within Japan, as well as performing at large rock festivals; the constant source of their drive and inspiration is without a doubt, from the audience. From me to you "BATON". From here, from now; it begins.\r\n\r\nSONG LIST\r\n1. The Fog\r\n2. Paradise of Wonderland\r\n3. The Abyss of My Deep Ocean\r\n4. The Frozen Lake\r\n5. The Harmony of The World', '2012-10-10 00:00:00', 0, 2, 8, 'START OF THE DAY', 'WONDER RAIN RECORDS', 0, '', 1, 0, '2013-06-05 09:47:24', '2015-02-16 15:48:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
